Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历1533.6\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 1533.6.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受命向运输船心大星号靠拢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now manoeuvring to come alongside cargo vessel Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,该船的船长和大副正向我舰传送中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its captain and first officer are beaming over to us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,随行的还有一位不寻常的乘客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with an unusual passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，士官长，开始物化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, chief. Begin materialisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拉马舰长，我是寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Ramart, I'm Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我的领航员汤姆·奈里斯 - 你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This is my navigator, Tom Nellis. - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 这位年轻人就是船难生还者，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How do you do? - This is our young castaway, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,全名查理·埃文斯，这是他的档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie Evans. His dossier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,埃文斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对你早有耳闻，欢迎登舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've heard a great deal about you. Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,查理是个好孩子，我们非常荣幸找到了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wonderful boy, Charlie. We felt honoured to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有他在舰上的日子很愉快，真的很愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been a pleasure having him. Why, it's been a great pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他所学的知识… - 绝对是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The things that he's learned-- - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想想这孩子几乎一个人在那星球生活了这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To think this boy's spent practically his whole life alone on that planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,无人幸存，只能从几卷微型卡带里学东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}everyone killed, just a few micro-tapes to learn from.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,船上有多少我这样的人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many humans like me on this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就像太空里的一座城市那么多，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like a whole city in space, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘星舰上有四百多船员，对吧，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Over 400 in the crew of a starship, aren't there, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,确切地说是四百二十八名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Four hundred and twenty-eight, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，需要什么帮助吗？药品，粮食补给？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there anything we can do for you, captain? Medical supplies, provisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,几百个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都是像我这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All human like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,太激动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是用这个词吗？ - 非常好，就是这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is that the right word? - That's perfect. It’s the exact word.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧见没？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.90,0:01:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们非常乐意带着查理一起航行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'd like to keep Charlie with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但和他关系最亲密的健在亲属在5号殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but with his closest living relatives on Colony V
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而且你们会路过那里，所以… - 我想现在就参观你的星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and your vessel going that way, why-- - I'd like to see your ship now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,全部，所有的人和东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All of it. The people and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直打断我们，埃文斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You keep interrupting, Mr. Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这么做可不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's considered wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，我们有大量的娱乐影音带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a large supply of entertainment tapes, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不了，舰长，我们行程颇紧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, we've a tight schedule to make, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们只有二十人，我们会搞定的 - 这一定是太空第一艘…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Just 20 of us. We're making out fine. - This must be a space first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么也不需要的舰船 - 真的不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A ship that doesn't need anything. - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,连蜥蜴酒也不要吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not even Saurian brandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不必了，谢谢，很高兴拜访至此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're fine, thank you. Pleasant journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德文书，这位是查理·埃文斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeoman Rand, this is Charles Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,带他去他的舱房，然后把他的档案放到麦考伊医生的办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Show him to his quarters and drop his records off at Dr. McCoy's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你愿意的话 - 好的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- if you will. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是女生吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她是女生吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她是女生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages Of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilisations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=THE LAST FANTASY=-荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：马田的心事，kmdangdangli，吴涵知\N校对：心痕依，Micezhang，xjCGI{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第二集\N神秘人查理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历1533.7\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 1533.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们迎来了一位不寻常的乘客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have taken aboard an unusual passenger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要把他送去阿尔法5号殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for transport to Colony Alpha V.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,查理·埃文斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charles Evans,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,十四年前一艘运输船坠毁后的唯一幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the sole survivor of a transport crash 14 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他不仅活了下来，且自三岁起就独自生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A child, alone from age 3, has not only survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现已成长为一名智聪体健的少年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but has grown to intelligent, healthy adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘船上的浓缩食物供给撑不过14年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the ship's supply of food concentrates couldn't have lasted 14 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,后来，我就找周围生长的东西吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After that, I found other things to eat just growing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,靠船上的卡带就学会说话了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you learned to talk by just listening to the ship's tapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆资料库还有用，他们和我说一句，我就回一句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The memory banks still worked. They talked to me, and I talked back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你得了四分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're 4-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,四分？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,四分就是满分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Four-0, 100 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,身体倍棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sound of wind and limb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那个舰长，叫寇克… - 怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That captain... Kirk? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么叫我埃文斯先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why does he call me Mr. Evans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那是你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because that's your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他和拉马舰长不同 - 不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, he isn't like Captain Ramart. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长可是独一无二的，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk is one of a kind, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有些…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的船员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不喜欢我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They didn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力让大家喜欢我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm trying to make people like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想要他们喜欢我 - 多数十七岁的孩子都这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I want them to like me. - Most 17-year-olds do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来，我们走，带你去看看你的舱房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on, let's go. I'll show you to your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把设备收好，娱乐室见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, I'll put the equipment away. See you in the Rec Room, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就这么定了，朋友 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You got a deal, friend. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你带了礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I brought you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢，但是…我得去值班了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I really appreciate it, but-- But I have to go. I’m on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢这种吗？ - 喜欢，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you like that kind? - Yes, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的最爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's my favourite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里弄来的，船上的仓储里没有这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where did you get it? They don't have any in the ship's stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,送你的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，但是你从哪里…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, but where did--?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我快迟到了，查理，我真得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gee, I'm late, Charlie. I really have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你能留下来陪我说会儿话吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't you stay and talk a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在1400时下班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I’m off duty at 14:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你去三号甲板的六号娱乐室找我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why don't you join me in Recreation Room 6, Deck 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么定了，朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got a deal, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别生气，我并不…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't be angry. I didn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想… - 查理，你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I wanted... - Charlie, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能随便拍女孩儿的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just don't go around slapping girls on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这次算了，但别再这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's okay, but just don't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别生气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，去和寇克舰长或者麦考伊医生谈谈刚才的事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, why don't you tell Captain Kirk or Dr. McCoy what you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会向你解释清楚的，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they'll explain it to you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会的 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I will. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，如果那有塔索斯人，他为什么要说谎？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But tell me, what reason would he have to lie if there are Thasians?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个问题很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is a very intriguing question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，传感器显示本象限无干扰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scanners show no disturbances in this quadrant, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，麦考伊医生，史波克正在制定…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. Dr. McCoy, Mr. Spock is working out--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打扰一下，舰长，这是状况报告 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Excuse me, captain, status report. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他正在为查理·埃文斯设计培训项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's working out a training programme for Charlie Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,包括地球史，以及他的种族背景之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth history, his own background, that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是希望你能从医学角度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like you to give him the necessary medical orientation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给予他一些必要的指导，关于…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the problems of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,关于青春期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得你更适合扮演父亲这个角色？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you think it'd be better for a father image like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他已经一切向你看齐了 - 这事归你了，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He already looks up to you. - The job is yours, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,阿谀奉承会使你一事无成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Flattery will get you nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，那孩子就一点都没提到塔索斯人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, didn't the boy make any reference at all to Thasians?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信塔索斯人仍以某种形式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you believe the legend
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,存活于那颗星球之上的传说吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that Thasians still exist on that planet in some form?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上，查理的存在就是塔索斯星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie's very existence proves, in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,存在某种智慧生命体的有力证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there must be some intelligent form of life on Thasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,仅靠自己他不可能生存下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He could not possibly have survived alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,船上的食物一年半载就消耗殆尽了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship's food would have been exhausted in a year or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那时，他可以靠水果蔬菜维生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By which time, he would've been eating fruits, vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对塔索斯星的探测表明，那里几乎没有可食用的植物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Probes of Thasus indicate very little edible plant life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，我们都知道探测器出过错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And probes have been known to be wrong, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，你是理智发言还是感情用事呐？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, are you speaking scientifically or emotionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，事实是，这孩子就在这活着，而且需要我们帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen. The fact is, the boy is here and he's alive and he needs our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而且需要指导，吉姆，他需要一位父亲的榜样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he needs a guide and he needs a father image, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我指望着你的聪明才智能去解决这一问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll depend on your astute abilities to supply him with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给他找一个也行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or find him one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我是不是又打扰到你了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry. I did it again, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,#在星舰进取号上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, on the starship Enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,#有一个伪装成撒旦模样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's someone Who's in Satan's guise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,#他那恶魔的耳朵，邪恶的双眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whose devil ears and devil eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,#能将你鲜活的心生生挖出胸膛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could rip your heart from you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,#目光触碰，他便将你催眠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At first his look could hypnotise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,#轻柔相抚，他便将你撕裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then his touch would barbarize
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,#他的异族之爱会深深地把你伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His alien love could victimize
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,#将你鲜活的心生生挖出胸膛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And rip your heart from you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,#所以飞天女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that's why female astronauts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,#美丽的飞天女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, very female astronauts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,#恐惧而又忧愁的等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait terrified and overwrought
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,#皆因了解面具下的他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To find what he will do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,#太空中的女孩要小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, girls in space be wary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,#小心啊，小心啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be wary, be wary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,#太空中的女孩要万分小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Girls in space be wary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,#他是一个谜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know not what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一曲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,#在那太空中的某颗星上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, from a planet out in space
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,#有位不一般的少年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There comes a lad Not commonplace
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,#只为找寻他的初恋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A-seeking out his first embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,#你就是他要找的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's saving it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,#查理是我们的新甜心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Charlie's our new darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,#我们的甜心，甜心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our darling, our darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,#查理是我们的新甜心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie's our new darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,#他是一个谜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know not what he'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你看些东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Want to see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,翻牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turn them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么办到的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我很会玩纸牌魔术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can do a lot of card tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,心大星号上的一个人教我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of the men on the Antares showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是地球上的感恩节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On Earth today, it's Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果船员不得不吃合成的肉卷，我希望它看上去像只火鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the crew has to eat synthetic meat loaf, I want it to look like turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 查理 - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Charlie. - Captain?
