Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我在走廊里看见…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, in the corridor, I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当贾尼丝…兰德文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When Janice... When Yeoman Rand was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么拍她了，她很反感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I did that to her, and she didn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她说你会向我解释清楚 - 我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She said you'd explain it to me. - Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，有些事情不能对女士做的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are things you can do with a lady, Charlie, that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不能拍打女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, there's no right way to hit a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说，男人拍打男人没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, man-to-man is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是男人拍打女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but man and woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就是另外一回事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it's another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你明白吗？ - 不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you understand? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克舰长 - 稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain Kirk. - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,心大星号舰长拉马正在D频道等候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Ramart of the Antares is on D channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上到舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm on my way to the bridge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能一起去吗？ - 不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Can I come? - I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不会妨碍你们 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I won't get in the way. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,心大星号，能否加强信号？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you boost your power, Antares?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们几乎接收不到你们的传输信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're barely reading your transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号，我们已经满额输出了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are at full output, Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须和寇克舰长通话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must speak to Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克，拉马舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here, Captain Ramart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，好不容易联系上你，我得警告…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, we're just barely in range. I've got to warn--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,重建通信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reestablish contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们没在发射信号 - 再试试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- They're not transmitting. - Well, try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘星舰构造不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't very well-constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,用我们的探测传感器扫描…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sweep the area of the Antares transmission
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 心大星号发出通讯的区域，史波克先生 - 收到，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- with our probe scanners, Mr. Spock. - Affirmative, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，你认为心大星出事了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you think something happened to the Antares, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，传感器探测到了些许残骸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Picking up some debris on our scanners, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那心大星号呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about the Antares?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那些就是心大星号的残骸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The debris is what's left of the Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克舰长，这里是星舰厨房 - 我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain Kirk, from ship's galley. - Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，之前我将肉卷放置在烤箱中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, I put meat loaf in the ovens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在它们变成了火鸡，真正的火鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's turkeys in there now. Real turkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,主厨，你是不是…？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chief, have you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历1535.8\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 1535.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,地球联邦空间探测总署已经宣布了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}UESPA headquarters notified of the mysterious loss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,科学探测船心大星号的神秘失踪 （心大星号是一艘多用途太空船，可用于运输、科学测量等）\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of science-probe vessel Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你的心思不在这盘棋上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your mind is not on the game, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在想心大星号？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Antares?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,二十人的测量船，全部罹难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A survey ship with 20 men aboard lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,原因不详\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,显然拉马舰长没有意识到丝毫危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously Captain Ramart was not aware of any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't figure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,眼下我更担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My own concern is more immediate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,通常我能理解你的意思，但这次…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can usually follow you, Mr. Spock, but this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎他比我们更早知道心大星号的结局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He seemed to know what happened to the Antares before we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,证据确凿，再下结论，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd call that a pretty long reach for evidence, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请进，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你输了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种没有章法的棋路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your illogical approach to chess
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有时的确厉害，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}does have its advantages on occasion, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我下棋都靠灵感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I prefer to call it inspired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是吧，反正你赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you wish. At any rate, the game is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,会下棋吗，查理？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you play chess, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…我在心大星号上见他们玩过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I-- I watched them play on the Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,能试试吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I try?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那就和这位象棋大师杀一盘吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I place you in the hands of our chess master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,三维象棋的游戏规则\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The principles of three-dimensional chess
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,基于数学，查理，白棋放这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are basically mathematic, Charlie. You put the white here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 黑棋在第二层 - 我知道怎么玩，开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and the black on the secondary level. - I know what it is. Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是个错着，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was a mistake, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我没走错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你输了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我没输\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，查理，我正找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Charlie, I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是蒂娜·劳顿，三级文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like you to meet Tina Lawton, yeoman, third class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 查理·埃文斯 - 你好，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Charlie Evans. - Hello, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你一定想认识些同龄人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you might enjoy meeting someone your own age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能和你聊聊吗？单独\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I talk to you? Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，蒂娜她…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie, Tina is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪了，别的地方总会欢迎我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me. I must be wanted somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚真是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太粗鲁，太不适宜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was rude and completely uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不需要她，我只想和你聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I don't need her. I wanna talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是借口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你得学会尊重人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'd better learn that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,学会跟人相处，查理，你不再是一个人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to live with people, Charlie. You're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但她没你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But she's not as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她不…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她和你不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她不像你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她…她只是个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's-- She's just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你闻上去如女孩般甜美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You smell like a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可舰上的其他女孩，她们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the other girls on the ship, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她们和蒂娜一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They look just like Tina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你最特别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're the only one who looks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我意思吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can understand, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那种寸步不离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know about being with somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想和一个人在一起的感觉吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wanting to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,若我拥有整个宇宙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I had the whole universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把它献给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I'd give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当我见到你，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I see you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一股冲动在心中燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I feel like I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如此地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,强烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那感觉吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know how that feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他说啥？！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我很犹豫该不该找你谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wasn't sure I should talk to you about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,文书，查理是个17岁的男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeoman, Charlie's a 17-year-old boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 正是，他还… - 我和他谈过他拍打你的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Exactly. And he's... - I talked to him about the swat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我了解那种眼神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I've seen the look before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,若置之不理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and if something isn't done,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟早会伤他的心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}sooner or later, I'm gonna have to hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他别来找我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell him to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他还小，对他不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that wouldn't be good for him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他一来就爱上我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, I'm his first crush,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我便是他的初恋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his first love,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他的第一次… - 知道了，文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and his first-- - Yes, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我找他谈，我会处理的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll talk to him. I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,进来，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,查理…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，你知道这棋子怎么了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie, do you know anything about this chess piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,注意到这颗棋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you notice anything peculiar in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 同之前有何不同吗？ - 没有，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...when we were using them? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没别的事了吧？ - 不…还有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is that all? - No. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，17岁不仅仅是个数字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie, being 17 is more than how many years you've lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还代表着别的含义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a whole other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生也许解释过生理的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy could probably explain the biological conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那我…我们就说个具体的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, let's-- Let's use a specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德文书是个女的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeoman Rand is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不会再拍打她了 - 不光是那件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I won't hit her like that anymore. - No, there's more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我说什么，做什么都是错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything I do or say is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.55,0:23:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨人厌，我不懂规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in the way. I don't know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我认真学，不管再努力还是一错再错！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I learn something and try to do it, suddenly, I’m wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 冷静点，慢慢说 - 我不知道自己是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Now, wait a minute. Wait a minute. - I don't know what I am
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,该成为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or what I’m supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至到底是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or even who.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为何我心里总是很难受？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know why I hurt so much inside all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,会好的，相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll live. Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的感受很正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's nothing wrong with you that hasn't gone wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,凡是男人都会经历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with every other human male since the model first came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你中意某人，会怎么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if you care for someone? What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你得慢慢来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You go slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.55,0:23:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你得…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:24:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,温柔地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,感情不是单方的，不能光顾你的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not a one-way street, you know. How you feel and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也要看对方的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's how the girl feels too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,强扭的瓜不甜，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't press, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,若对方也喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the girl feels anything for you at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自然会告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you'll know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.03,0:24:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说贾尼丝…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't think Jan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,文书…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeo--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.75,0:24:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她会爱上我的！ - 你们不合适，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She could love me! - She's not the girl, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.67,0:24:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们年龄悬殊，这是其一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The years are wrong, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And there are other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她会的 - 不，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She can. - No, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.09,0:24:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她会的 - 不可能！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She is. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那我听你的，我会温柔的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if I did what you said, if I was gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.18,0:24:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，在这宇宙你可以拥有很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are a million things in this universe you can have,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.60,0:24:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也有很多东西一辈子注定不能拥有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and there are a million things you can't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.68,0:24:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,现实就这么残酷，除了面对，别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's no fun facing that, but that's the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.77,0:24:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来我该怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, then what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.27,0:24:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,咬紧牙，活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hang on tight and survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.23,0:24:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everybody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.36,0:25:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你就不是 - 每个人，查理，包括我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You don't. - Everybody, Charlie. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.12,0:25:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可就是不得要领\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but I don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是寇克 - 报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk here. - You asked to be notified
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.59,0:25:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,航向即将调整，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when we were to make our course adjustments, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.80,0:25:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让史波克大副负责此事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask Mr. Spock to see to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.47,0:25:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie, come on with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.12,0:25:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,倒向地面来缓冲你摔倒时的冲力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gotta slap the floor to absorb the energy when you fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.49,0:25:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,试试吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go ahead, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.96,0:25:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,凡事得多练，查理，再来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like everything else it takes practise, Charlie. Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.42,0:26:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.88,0:26:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我会示范一个肩膀滚翻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, now I'll show you a shoulder roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.98,0:26:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,试试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.85,0:26:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't wanna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.44,0:26:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这样我会教不好… - 我不想做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, it makes it hard to teach you-- - I don't wanna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.40,0:26:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，查理，今天就学到这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, Charlie, lesson's over for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.69,0:26:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你答应教我格斗的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were gonna teach me how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.24,0:26:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你得先学会跌倒时的自我保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to learn to protect yourself from the fall before I do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.41,0:26:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我再教你自我防卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's more than just teaching you how to defend yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.70,0:26:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，我想让你学会…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie, I want you to learn--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.87,0:26:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.04,0:26:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，山姆，配合我摔几个？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Sam, let me borrow you for a couple of easy throws, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.59,0:26:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊 - 看好了，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- All right. - Watch this, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.81,0:26:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么坏，是不？现在换我摔他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wasn't so bad, was it? Now I'll throw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.93,0:26:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好，山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here we go, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.23,0:27:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去很难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That looks hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.90,0:27:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,加油，查理，试试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on, Charlie, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.03,0:27:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attaboy. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.79,0:27:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这不难吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wasn't so bad, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.39,0:27:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别笑我 - 别在意，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Don't laugh at me. - Cool off, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.85,0:27:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要取笑我！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't laugh at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.46,0:28:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.84,0:28:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他不该那样对我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.13,0:28:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,取笑别人是不对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not nice to laugh at people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.76,0:28:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么了，查理？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened to him, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.84,0:28:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.39,0:28:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.77,0:28:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.60,0:28:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想这样，是他逼我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't mean to do that. He made me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.48,0:28:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他笑我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He laughed at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.40,0:28:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥 - 我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bridge. - Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.82,0:28:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里需要两名安全人员，尽快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two men from Security on the double.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.41,0:28:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 收到 - 你要对我做什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Affirmative. - What are you going to do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.49,0:28:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,待在你的舱房，面壁思过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm confining you to quarters. I want you to stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.66,0:28:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让他们伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't let them hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.00,0:28:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会让他们也消失 - 他们不会伤害你，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'll make them go away too. - They won't hurt you, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.39,0:28:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会送你回舱房，查理，跟他们回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll take you to your quarters, Charlie. Go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.35,0:28:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.95,0:29:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,回你的舱房去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go to your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.37,0:29:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚才想伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was going to hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.70,0:29:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,回你的舱房，否则我亲自把你拎回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go to your quarters, or I'll pick you up and carry you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.53,0:29:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你得逞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.20,0:29:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就别怪我不客气，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's your choice, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.96,0:29:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让他们伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't let them hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.59,0:29:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.43,0:30:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.60,0:30:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.73,0:30:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,安全部报告，所有相位武器都消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security reports that all phaser weapons have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.40,0:30:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,需要重复吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shall I repeat, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.48,0:30:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我听清了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.07,0:30:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让麦考伊医生和史波克大副到简报室见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have Dr. McCoy and Mr. Spock meet me in the Briefing Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.37,0:30:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,据记载，塔索斯人[非实体生物族群，居住在塔索斯星球]\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thasians have been referred to in our records
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.93,0:30:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能让物体嬗变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as having the power to transmute objects
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.21,0:30:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,或消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or render substances invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.51,0:30:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这虽只是个传说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has generally been regarded as legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.47,0:30:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但查理似乎的确拥有这种能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but Charlie does seem to possess this same power.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.47,0:30:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,难道查理并非人类而是塔索斯人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What chance is there that Charlie isn't an Earth being, that he's a Thasian?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.85,0:30:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.10,0:30:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,除非它们和地球人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not unless they're exactly like earthlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.31,0:30:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他手指和脚趾的发育\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The development of his fingers and toes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.93,0:30:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,和同龄地球人一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}exactly matches the present development of man's on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.69,0:30:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有道理 - 但不论他是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Agreed. - But whatever he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.36,0:31:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他的能力我们已有所了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we have some idea of the power he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.40,0:31:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲眼目睹他在健身房的所作所为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what I saw him do in the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.74,0:31:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到一个家庭对一个普通青少年的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Considering the effect a normal adolescent has on a home,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.20,0:31:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，所具备…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie, with the power he has...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.95,0:31:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,暴躁的脾气，因为他还不明世事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Short-tempered, because he doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.28,0:31:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他既冲动又渴望，不会走就想跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He needs, he wants. Nothing happens fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.79,0:31:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,心大星号的毁灭可能和他有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The probability is, he's responsible for the destruction of the Antares,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他还不懂得尊重生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which would indicate a total disregard for human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.67,0:31:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会明白生命的意义，他就是个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He doesn't understand what life is. He's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那如何对付这个孩子，吉姆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, what do we do with this boy, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 关他的禁闭？ - 这还远远不够，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How do we keep him caged up? - It goes even further than that, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.97,0:31:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没法带他去5号殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't take him with us to Earth Colony V.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.47,0:31:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想象他在一个开放、正常的环境里做出什么吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you imagine what he'd do in an open, normal environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.81,0:31:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我循循善诱，用心倾听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've talked with him. I've listened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.27,0:31:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他身体成熟，可心智稚嫩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a boy in a man's body, trying to be an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.07,0:31:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,正值青春期，却一心想做个大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the adolescent in him getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.24,0:31:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他可怕的能力能置人于死地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And with a weapon in him, which could destroy you or anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.45,0:31:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他能杀死这艘星舰上的任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}anywhere on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.91,0:31:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好在眼下他停住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, for the moment, he's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.12,0:32:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他很崇拜你，吉姆 - 我也这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're an authority he respects, Jim. - Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.50,0:32:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你才能说服得了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The struggle must remain between you and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.09,0:32:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,万一我们之中有人插手这件事…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Should any of us interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.01,0:32:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你想问我点事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You wanted to ask me something, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.14,0:32:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，心大星号的事是不是你干的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you responsible for what happened to the Antares, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.19,0:32:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？ - 回答我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why? - Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.36,0:32:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.11,0:32:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在能源反应堆的防护罩上有一块变形了的折流档板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was a warped baffle plate on the shield of their energy pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.32,0:32:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我让它消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I made it go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.53,0:32:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,迟早都会爆炸的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would have blown up anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.83,0:32:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们对我一点也不好！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, they weren't nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.71,0:32:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要把我赶走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They wanted to get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.63,0:32:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在办不到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They don't now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.63,0:32:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们呢，查理？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about us, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.89,0:32:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.74,0:33:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们落入青春期少年手里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're in the hands of an adolescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.12,0:33:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，接5号殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant, raise Colony V.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.08,0:33:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要直接和他们的总督通话 - 遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I want to speak to the governor. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.25,0:33:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,领航员，制定路线，离开5号殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Navigator, lay in a course away from Colony V.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.37,0:33:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 争取时间 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Buy me some time. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.88,0:33:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，让医生尽快过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, get the doctor up here on the double.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.84,0:33:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,严重吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.76,0:33:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，我还好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think it's all right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.89,0:33:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，那块控制板不可能这样无缘无故的短路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, there's no reason for that panel to cross-circuit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.60,0:33:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不到15分钟前，我还亲自检查过的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I checked it over myself not 15 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.02,0:33:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.27,0:33:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，我无法在控制板输入航线坐标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't feed any course coordinates into the panel, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.77,0:33:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它不接受任何航线改动了 - 长官，船舵也没有反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It rejects the course change. - Helm doesn't respond either, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.86,0:33:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，你那边有读数吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, you getting any readings on your instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.45,0:33:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官，有一个…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir. There's a--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.62,0:33:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老虎！老虎！黑夜的森林中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tiger, tiger, burning bright
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.16,0:34:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,燃烧着的煌煌的火光 （来自威廉·布莱克的《老虎》）\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the forest of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.79,0:34:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克？ - 我正要…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock? - I'm trying to--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.83,0:34:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,脑海环绕着土星，游荡在火星的红色之路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Saturn rings around my head Down a road that's Martian red
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.13,0:34:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你想要改变航线吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're trying to change course, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.42,0:34:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能那么做，我想快点到5号殖民地去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't do that. I want to get to Colony V as soon as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.52,0:34:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让通讯发射器恢复正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Release the transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.52,0:34:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你用不着听那些子空间的杂音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't need all that subspace chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.40,0:34:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里发生了什么事儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.90,0:34:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克叫我到舰桥来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock calls me to the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.23,0:34:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 话还没说完就开始吟什么诗了… - 照看一下她，麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and then goes into poetry. - See to her, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.49,0:34:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从前一个阴郁的子夜，我独自沉思，慵懒疲竭 (来自爱伦坡《乌鸦》)\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Once upon a midnight dreary, while I pondered, weak and weary
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.57,0:34:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的，尖耳朵先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very nice, Mr. Ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.12,0:34:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以让他做任何事，转圈，大笑，所有事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I can make him do anything. Whirl around, laugh, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.62,0:34:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,够了，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's enough, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.00,0:34:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得他很好笑吗？我觉得他好笑极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you think he's funny? I think he's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.00,0:34:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别动我的船员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leave my crew alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.81,0:35:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，很快他就会抗拒你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, he'll soon reach a point where he won't back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.90,0:35:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.36,0:35:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.26,0:35:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有样东西要给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.90,0:35:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你最喜欢粉色，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pink is your favourite, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.40,0:35:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能不敲门就进别人房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't walk into a room without knocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.82,0:36:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,贾尼丝，别再对我锁上你的门，我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't ever lock your door on me again, Janice. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.25,0:36:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想锁就锁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll lock it when I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.12,0:36:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想要什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it you want, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.75,0:36:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.03,0:36:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想对你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I only want to be nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.90,0:36:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你告诉我，我什么都可以给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can give you anything. Just-- Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.16,0:36:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.70,0:36:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我只是想对你好而已 - 出去，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I only want to be nice to you. - Get out, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.24,0:36:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克 - 我说的已经很清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock. - I can't make it any plainer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.92,0:36:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.29,0:36:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道这句话的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't know what the word means.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.21,0:36:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你教我 - 不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Then show me. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.52,0:36:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.99,0:37:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她为什么这么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.71,0:37:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱她…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I loved her...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.05,0:37:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,…但她对我一点也不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but she wasn't nice at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.55,0:37:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们对我也不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you did wasn't nice either.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.93,0:37:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我仍然需要你，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I still need you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.60,0:37:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号和心大星号不太一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Enterprise isn't quite like the Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.39,0:37:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,控制心大星号很容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Running the Antares was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.40,0:37:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们最好友善点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.90,0:37:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.09,0:37:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.80,0:37:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.68,0:38:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,断掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.76,0:38:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，也放了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let him go too, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.97,0:38:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？ - 因为我要你放了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why? - Because I'm telling you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.19,0:38:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你需要我操纵这艘星舰，而我需要他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you need me to run the ship, and I need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.51,0:38:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你再想伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you try to hurt me again,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.29,0:38:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让更多的人消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll make a lot of people go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.21,0:38:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,贾尼丝文书怎么样了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And what about Yeoman Janice?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.71,0:38:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她死了，还是消失了，还是被毁灭了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is she dead, gone, destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.51,0:38:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.31,0:38:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,长大也没什么了不起的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Growing up isn't so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.48,0:38:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是大人，照样可以做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not a man, and I can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.94,0:38:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你却不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.69,0:39:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[空气系统]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.31,0:39:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我来启动力场，你可以回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll activate the force field myself. You can return to your section.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.73,0:39:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他表情很恶心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He had a mean look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.61,0:39:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我把他定住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had to freeze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.36,0:39:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢高兴的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I like happy looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.74,0:39:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不进来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aren't you coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.10,0:39:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That wasn't nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.02,0:39:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会后悔的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.94,0:39:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧，你们会后悔这么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You wait, you'll see. You'll be sorry you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.65,0:39:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会后悔的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.10,0:40:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.47,0:40:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不准笑！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.41,0:40:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长，我的仪器显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk, my instruments show
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.41,0:40:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在接收来自子空间频率3的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we're receiving a message on subspace frequency three,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.58,0:40:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舰对舰通讯信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ship to ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.13,0:40:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但我听不到，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't hear it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.80,0:41:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，你是在发讯息还是在阻挡我们接收那条讯息？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you creating that message, or are you blocking one that's coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.68,0:41:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，这是我的游戏，你自己去想吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's my game, captain. You have to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.89,0:41:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,正如你所说的，游戏就是这么玩的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like you said, that's how the game's played.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.47,0:41:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在归你了，我已经把航线又锁定回5号殖民地了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can have it now. I've locked on course for Colony V again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.38,0:41:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我等的够长了，我要拿下他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've waited long enough. I'm gonna take him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.47,0:41:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他没有任何特殊的抵抗力，不再有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have any special immunity. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.68,0:41:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把他逼急了，他会让你也消失的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Push far enough, he'd send you off to oblivion too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.73,0:41:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克？ - 没可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock? - Out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.19,0:41:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.27,0:42:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,查理他…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is Charlie--?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.32,0:42:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不对，等等，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, wait. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.95,0:42:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他接管星舰之后，有谁消失了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has he done away with anybody since he took over?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.57,0:42:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就我们所知，没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not so far as we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.62,0:42:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定他办不到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then maybe he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.33,0:42:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能达到极限了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could be he's overreached himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.83,0:42:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘舰船很大，他已经全盘控制了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a big ship. He's taken full control.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.88,0:42:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们可以加重他的负担\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we could tax his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.26,0:42:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把船上的每个装置、每条电路、每盏灯都打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}turn on every device on the ship, every circuit, every light, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.39,0:42:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在他应付这些东西的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And while he's fighting that,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.26,0:42:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我从旁让他分心，你们就可以给他打镇定剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I could distract him, maybe you could tranquilize him
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.22,0:42:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,控制住他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and keep him under
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.98,0:42:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我们到达5号殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until we reach Colony V.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.27,0:42:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很冒险，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Risky, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.65,0:42:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不试试，麦考伊，他会让我们所有人都消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we don't try, doctor, he'll get rid of us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.95,0:42:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别无选择，先生们，完全没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no choice, gentlemen, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.16,0:42:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我想让你们消失，你们就会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can make you all go away, any time I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.17,0:42:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,从我的椅子上下来，查理，马上下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get out of my chair, Charlie, and get out of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.58,0:42:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的船在我手里，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got your ship, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.22,0:43:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe, Charlie,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.22,0:43:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得你没法掌控更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I don't think you can handle any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.94,0:43:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你已经到极限了，多一样都不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you've reached your limit and can't take on one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.28,0:43:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但你却不得不这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you're gonna have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.87,0:43:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我早可以让你消失，但我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could have sent you away before, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.96,0:43:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那就干掉我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're gonna have to take me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.17,0:43:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别逼我这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't make me do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.26,0:43:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你抢了我的船，我现在要把它夺回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got my ship, and I want it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.84,0:43:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我的船员回来，所有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want my crew back, whole...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.31,0:43:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是非得拧断你的脖子才能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...if I have to break your neck to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.61,0:43:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要逼我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.33,0:44:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.16,0:44:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉，但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.51,0:44:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.05,0:44:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你们住手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.98,0:44:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，导航控制台的障碍已经清除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, navigation console is clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.48,0:44:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰对舵轮也有反应了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship is answering the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.52,0:44:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，我们的右舷船头前方有不明物体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, something off our starboard bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.53,0:44:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,讯息说他们来自塔索斯星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The message says they're from Thasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.32,0:44:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.12,0:44:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长，我怎么会？ - 已经没事了，文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain, how did I...? - It's all right, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.16,0:44:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,传感器显示那儿有不明物体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensors show there's something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.12,0:44:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,偏导仪显示没有实体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Deflectors indicate no solid substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.96,0:44:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.84,0:44:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，不，求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.18,0:44:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他们把我带走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't let them take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.35,0:45:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法忍受再跟他们一起生活了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't live with them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.98,0:45:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.11,0:45:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说过是我的朋友，记得吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said you were my friends, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.20,0:45:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在我刚来的时候！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I came aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.00,0:45:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.42,0:45:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.72,0:45:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,带我回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.52,0:45:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,几个世纪前，我已经抛弃了我的形体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have taken my form centuries ago
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.23,0:45:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于需要这样我才能和你们交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so that I may communicate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.15,0:45:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,意识到这个孩子跑了，已经太迟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We did not realise until too late that the boy had gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.86,0:46:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,致使第一艘舰船的全体船员丧命，我们对此感到非常痛心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we are saddened that his escape cost the lives of the first ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.20,0:46:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们帮不了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We could not help them,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.54,0:46:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但已经把你们的人和船都归还给你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we have returned your people and your ship to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.88,0:46:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一切如初\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything is as it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.05,0:46:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.47,0:46:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，我会听话的，我不会再这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, I'll be good. I won't ever do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.90,0:46:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,心大星号的事是我的错，对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry about the Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.03,0:46:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.45,0:46:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,求你让我留在船上！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I came aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.70,0:46:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,求你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.66,0:46:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和你一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.62,0:46:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.89,0:47:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子属于他自己的种族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The boy belongs with his own kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.98,0:47:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That will be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.81,0:47:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会教他在我们的社会中生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can teach him to live in our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.19,0:47:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他可以学会不使用他的超能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he can be taught not to use his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.15,0:47:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给了他超能力让他能够生存下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We gave him the power so he could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.28,0:47:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他总会使用它的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He will use it, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.70,0:47:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他会毁灭你和你的种族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he would destroy you and your kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.45,0:47:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你就得杀了他，来拯救你们自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or you would be forced to destroy him to save yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.33,0:47:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没有其他办法了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there nothing you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.17,0:47:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给了他生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We offer him life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.34,0:47:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们会照顾好他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.59,0:47:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.44,0:47:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.35,0:47:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他们带走我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't let them take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.48,0:48:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本就无法触摸到他们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't even touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.61,0:48:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,贾尼丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Janice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.03,0:48:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They can't feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.74,0:48:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不像你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.75,0:48:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会去爱！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They don't love!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.21,0:48:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.42,0:48:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.76,0:48:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,留下来，留下，留…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay, stay, stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.36,0:48:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,查理已经回到塔索斯人的船上了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charlie's back onboard the Thasian ship, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.99,0:48:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发讯号说他们离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They signalled they're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.21,0:49:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的，文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's all right, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.42,0:49:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.76,0:49:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,本集结束
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.82,0:49:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏
